Package: plotthis
Title: An R Package Built Upon `ggplot2` and Other Plotting Packages
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R:
    person("Panwen", "Wang", , "pwwang@pwwang.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4614-8970"))
Description: `plotthis` is an R package that is built upon `ggplot2` and other plotting packages. It provides high-level APIs and a wide range of options to create stunning, publication-quality plots effortlessly.
